Description:
Immaculate Family Home
Whether you are looking to get into your first home, starting your portfolio or adding to it, this three bedroom home is fantastic value. Situated on a large 553m2 allotment and located within walking distance to schooling and amenities this property represents great value for any purchaser. On entry you are greeted by a generously sized formal lounge room. The three well proportioned bedrooms are serviced by the centrally located family bathroom, kitchen/meals area has excellent cupboard space. Laundry and separate toilet round out this beautifully kept family home. Outside we have a large secure north facing rear yard, single garage and garden shed. This property will tick all the boxes. Inspection a must!

Description:
Buy One, Buy Both! What An Opportunity.
The chance to purchase 2 homes side by side is a rare and highly sought after one. Here is an opportunity to purchase 40 and 42 Caithness Crescent and build your portfolio and look to the future. Beautifully presented and with nothing to do other than decide where to place your furniture this outstanding home sets the bar for the highest standard of living at a very affordable price. This solid home set on app. 670 sqm. is comprised of 3 large bedrooms, master with built in robes and quality wall to wall carpet and ceiling fan, central living room with polished floorboards, reverse cycle heating and cooling unit and impressive downlights. The tastefully updated kitchen and meals area is equipped with dishwasher, gas oven and cook top plus plenty of storage and bench space and opens out to a massive undercover outdoor entertainment area and a versatile double garage that would also be perfect as a man cave/second entertainment room. The central bathroom has undergone a tasteful update and has a separate shower and bath plus quality tiling and fittings. Currently tenanted at $270 per week this property is an outstanding long term investment proposition or as an ideal first home.

Description:
Look No Further!!
Completely renovated four bedroom brick family home situated in a quiet court location. As you enter you are welcomed by the open plan living with gas heating and split system, followed by the meals area and updated kitchen with ample cupboard and storage space including stainless steel appliances and dishwasher. The main bedroom and two other bedrooms all with built-in-robes situated off the hallway, along with the study or forth bedroom or formal dining. Separate laundry and bathroom with shower and bath and separate toilet. North facing manicured gardens with double garage and fabulous entertaining area. Conveniently located close to the Ring Road, Shopping Centres, public transport, schools and the local park at your doorstep, situated on approx. 689m2 block. Simply move straight in with nothing to do or add to your growing investment portfolio.

Description:
Neat Three Bedroom Home on a Big Block!
Residing on approximately 626m2 of land, this well-kept single level BV three-bedroom home offers a sensational opportunity to secure a home with the potential to renovate, extend or redevelop (STCA) or just enjoy as is.
With ducted heating throughout, the traditional floor plan incorporates a comfortable family lounge room with air conditioning unit, that guide you to the well-appointed kitchen with open plan dining. All three bedrooms include built in robes and bathroom is complete with spa bath, shower and toilet.
The large, secure backyard makes this home perfect for the growing family whilst taking advantage of the garden shed and large undercover area for entertaining.
This property offers excellent off-street parking with an impressive large side drive way with side gate access to double lock up garage.
Spoilt for choice with all necessities and more at your fingertips, which include schools, public transport, shopping centres and easy access to the Ring Road. With so much happening in the growth corridor, this property offers great potential and a fantastic opportunity.
Currently leased to a potential long term tenant that maintains the property exceptionally well.

Description:
Renovated Home Close To Schools & Shops
Set on 607sqm of land, this renovated home is ready for its new owners. With a subtle colour palette and modern updates, everything has been done for you so you can move in and enjoy this great home. The floorplan offers three good-sized bedrooms and one bathroom, a great kitchen with plenty of storage and modern appliances, plus a large, light-filled living room with gas heating and air-conditioning. A laundry and built-in linen closet complete the floorplan. Step outside to the huge backyard. Fully-fenced, there is plenty of room for the kids and family pet to run free or for the green thumb to indulge in landscaped gardens. A free-standing garage provides extra storage space. Schools, shops and public transport are all within walking distance so you will never need to travel far to access everything you need. Set on a quiet street with the opportunity to secure two properties side by side for a total of 1214sqm in the "residential growth zone", this is a great development opportunity for the future.

Description:
Room to grow.
This outstanding and spacious family residence has been meticulously cared for and under gone a huge renovation with large extension, positioned perfectly on a large allotment of 720m2 (approx.). Boasting an enormous floorplan that offers multiple living zones and flexibility for the growing family. Showcasing three bedrooms on the ground floor serviced by the central bathroom while the master suite at the front of the residence comes complete with personal ensuite and walk in robe. The large lounge upon entrance is adjoined by a sitting area that opens up onto the outdoor alfresco. At the centre of the home you'll find the original kitchen overlooking a meals area that precedes a second spacious living area and second kitchen situated at the rear of the home. Moving to the first floor you'll find an additional bedroom complete with ensuite and living area with access to the balcony. Off street parking is available via the large side driveway with DLUG which also contains a large storage area. Enjoy seamless indoor/outdoor entertaining in the large backyard that features a built in wood fire. Nestled in the much sought after Cloverdale estate the home is surrounded by multiple reserves and provides easy access to the Ring Road, primary schools and Corio Shopping Centre all just a 2 minute drive away. This extroadinary and unique property provides an amazing opportunity for families searching for the perfect home that offers an abundance of living space in a highly desirable area.

Description:
The Family Entertainer!
The essence of stylish, low maintenance living is on show in this well-appointed residence. Offering a sought-after and convenient lifestyle with easy Ring Road access and moments from shops and public transport, this chic family home offers wonderful zoned living and entertaining spaces including large lounge room and family/living room. A great functional kitchen features 90cm gas hot plate, electric oven and dishwasher. Segmented double-door pantry and wrap-around bench with breakfast bar add enhanced appeal. Three robed bedrooms and a home office are serviced by main bathroom with separate shower and bath; master features ensuite and walk-in-robe. Comprehensive appointments include timber floorboards throughout; wall heater, split system inverter and ceiling fans; solar panels, security doors and off-street parking. Set amidst manicured gardens in a sprawling backyard, a paved uncover area provides ideal options for outdoor dining and entertaining. Two garden sheds and a cubby house complete this home. Arrange inspection today!

Description:
Upgrade Your Living
This spacious family home has been remodelled from front to back creating a terrific opportunity for first home buyers, families and investors alike. Impeccably presented inside, it's the perfect balance between contemporary living and modern convenience. Offering three generous bedrooms, a light filled study and central kitchen/meals area that opens up to both the living room and separate lounge. Overlooking the main lounge the sleek kitchen offers walk in pantry and stainless steel appliances including a 900mm gas stove. The bathroom with its floating vanity and frameless glass, walk-in shower create a luxe look and feel. Set on 610sqm of land, this beautiful home also has a great size backyard allowing plenty of space for the kids and pets to play. Added benefits include the lock-up garage and carport with ample off street parking for a boat or caravan. Located within walking distance to Corio Village, primary and secondary schools, public transport and with easy access to the Ring Road this home is a must see!

Description:
Updated And Convenient
Neat and tidy, this centrally located home offers easy-care living perfect for investors and downsizers. The open-plan lounge room with north facing floor-to-ceiling windows allowing the space to be bathed in light flows to the updated and well-equipped kitchen offering gas cooking, plenty of storage and a breakfast bar for casual dining. The two bedrooms, both with built-in robes, a simple yet functional bathroom and internal laundry providing access to the courtyard complete the floorplan. The private courtyard is perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or soaking up the sunshine. The addition of a separate carport and storage space offers further convenience. This move-in ready villa is located within a well-maintained complex. You can leave the car at home and walk to the local doctors and public transport options, while Corio Village shopping centre is only a few minutes away. This property presents great value.

Description:
More Than Meets The Eye
This lovely 3 bedroom property has been extended & updated to provide the next family with a lovely home ready to move into, unpack & enjoy.
All three bedrooms have polished floorboards & are located close to the family bathroom & updated laundry. The central timber kitchen has ample bench space, large pantry & stainless appliances including dishwasher. A large family dining room flows from the kitchen into the spacious lounge room which leads to the undercover private deck.

Description:
Perfectly positioned.
Let your imagination run wild with this outstanding development opportunity in the heart of Corio. This enormous allotment represents unique possibilities for all builders and first home buyers to make their mark on this up and coming suburb.
As Corio is forever expanding, position of property is everything.
This beautiful home is situated in the heart of it all, within walking distance to Corio shopping centre, local schools, sporting facilities, childcare centres, healthcare professionals and the Western Ring Road Practically at your doorstep what more could you desire.
Comprising of three good sized bedrooms all with floorboards, central tiled bathroom, retro styled kitchen with plenty of cupboard space, large carpeted formal lounge upon entry, single garage and separate carport. An undercover alfresco area at the rear end of the house accompanied by a largely grassed backyard is perfect for the kids to run and play or future development prospects (STCA)...all on a fantastic allotment of 1,010m2 (approx).
This home offers so much potential for the right buyer or investors alike! Buy today and reap the rewards tomorrow!
** PLEASE NOTE: Photos used for advertising are from the previous sale of the home. Please call to inspect the property in person and its current condition.

Description:
When potential & opportunity combine.
This three bedroom brick veneer home on a corner allotment presents an irresistible invitation to astute buyers as it is currently tenanted at $250pw, or keen renovators who will warm to the original proportions and solid foundation on offer. Including a comfortable lounge upon entrance which leads to the kitchen and meals area. The three bedrooms in total (2 with BIR'S) are easily accessible to the central bathroom and separate laundry. Sitting on an impressive 601m2 (approx.) allotment outside provides a sizeable grassed rear yard, SLUG and carport. Situated across the road from the Rosewall Reserve the home is conveniently located a short drive to the Princes Highway, sporting facilities, and local shopping services. Certainly an ideal home for those looking to jump into the market, this property should be at the top of your inspection list.

Description:
Investors dream.
An ideal opportunity for those in search of their next project or development in the booming suburb of Corio offering a magnificent 1043m2 (approx.) allotment with a three bedroom home that's currently tenanted for $200pw.
Offering a wide side driveway, forward positioned home and extensive rear yard this property is ideal for those looking to potentially sub-divide and construct an additional dwelling in the rear (STCA) or hold as an addition to your investment portfolio. Comprising of three bedrooms in total, comfortable lounge, central bathroom and kitchen with meals area.
The large rear yard provides the new owners the chance to transform this prime piece of land into a future development site (STCA) otherwise leave as is and hold for future growth. Overlooking the Princes Highway set behind a slip lane the home provides easy access to the Corio Shopping Centre, Primary Schools and child care facilities make this home easily accessible to most major amenities.

Description:
Fab First Home, Solid Investment or Ideal Downsizer
This solid 3 bed, 1 bath, 1 huge living, 4 car brick home set on 585 m2 block will suit an array of buyers.
Situated in a growth corridor of Corio, minutes to the freeway and 10 minutes to Geelong CBD.
This solid brick home is spacious and modern. Comprising of a wonderful sized open plan dining / kitchen space equipped with gas 4 burner stove, SS appliances and ample cupboards. Adjacent to the kitchen is a huge oversize family room equipped with AC, ceiling fan and wonderful natural light. Making it a great space for the whole family to unwind in.
Down the hall you will find 3 great sized bedrooms all with BIR and large Master with AC system and modern ceiling fan. The central bathroom is bright and spacious and comes with modern corner spa bath, separate shower and toilet.
All front facing windows are fitted with electric blinds ideal for privacy, security and any weather conditions.
Outside you will find a neat back deck and spacious rear yard ideal for pets, children or entertaining. There is also ample parking with a double garage at the rear plus carport, fitting an additional 2 cars.

Description:
Sensational Opportunity In A Fantastic Location
This property is an exciting opportunity for families, investors and developers alike. Set on a 607sqm block, the neighbouring property is also for sale. Therefore presenting a combined 1214sqm of land in the high-density growth zone across two titles. Inside, there's plenty of room for everyone with the home being extended to offer 4 bedrooms, three with built-in robes, two living spaces and an updated central bathroom. At the heart of the home the open plan lounge and updated kitchen and meals area offers air-conditioning and a gas heater for year round comfort. Outside, the north facing backyard has ample space, a free-standing garage and so much potential. Perfectly positioned within walking distance to Corio Shopping centre and all it has to offer, local schools, medical clinics, transport and great access to the Ring Road, you can't afford to miss this opportunity.
Due Diligence checklist are available at www.consumer.vic.gov.au/duediligencechecklist
